data.description: Welcome home to 355 Erie Drive.  UPDATED 3 bed 2 bath Ranch Home centrally located with easy access to I 24, Wilma Rudolph and Fort Campbell. New roof, kitchen cabinets, soap stone counter tops, tile backsplash, carpet in bedrooms, tile in bathroom floors, tiled shower in primary, toilets & vanities. Fresh paint. New deck all new fixtures. Detached 2 car garage w/ wood burning stove great for a shop. Includes carport and outdoor shed Early occupancy maybe considered. Home is on a cul-de-sac!
